message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with image-based question-answering using neural networks and visual semantic embeddings, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of algorithms for question generation (cs.AI) and presents baseline results (cs.LG) on a new dataset. Finally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with answering questions based on visual information.
